snippet.title: Bombrigade: Battlegrounds | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Violence has never been so cute! Bombrigade delivers explosive arcade action with up to 50 players in a single match. Coming to PC and mobile March 13th.
【Social Media, Beta Access, and More Info】
Website: https://bombrigade.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/bombrigade
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Bombrigade
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bombrigade/
Steam Store: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1096310/Bombrigade_Battlegrounds

Official Discord: https://discord.gg/P3bx4Sr

Music: PLEEG - Next Level (Twitter: https://twitter.com/pleegmusic)
